				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10117202#post-4133902</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10117202/scp-3462#post-4133902</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 28 Jan 2019 22:01:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deadly Bread</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3988532</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Information can't last forever. Neither can Blockbuster I guess. This was a highly ambitious rewrite of my former article <em>The Subliminal Little Toaster</em>, with barely anything resembling the original SCP. This is also my first Keter class SCP, so that's exciting. Huge thanks to both <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2048131&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596428971" alt="Proasek" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2048131)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" >Proasek</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=224440&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596428971" alt="AdminBright" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=224440)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" >AdminBright</a></span> for their criticism in the early stages of this mess. I hope you all enjoy, and you might see more from the Television Tax Collectors in a future article.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-bread-box">Other Articles of Mine</a></p> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
